metadata.name: W3 ART - ACC3SS PASS #1
metadata.description:
Holders of the W3 ART Pass have a front row seat to the transformation of art as it enters the metaverse. 
By becoming a W3 ART Pass holder, you support the curation of daring artists and the technology that powers our collective future. 
FOUND3R Pass holders receive lifetime access to unique perks, including early access to W3 ART productions. 
MEMB3R Pass holders have the same benefits for a one-year period that starts at the time of minting.
